phrases: Let me test out my new move on you!
I call it the 120 - Hour Beating!
One, two, hey, yo, let us dance!
Hey come on, it will be fine!
They are so cute, are not they Shiina - san?
What is this, an elementary school?
Fine, I will go ask Oyama - senpai!
All we do is take on more brats.
Are you talking to me, scum?
You were clinging onto Otonashi and crying like a baby.
The one crying will be you.
Now, you will realize the greatness of clothespins,
and in comparison, your worthlessness, and despair.
You pin it and it does not fall...
The laundry does not get dirty!
You can use it instead of a paper clip or just about anything else!
I am nothing compared to it!
There is no hope for me at all!
Hey, do not use hypnotism to fight back.
What did you do to him?
What part of that is gentle?
You have a grown man on his knees crying like a baby.
Come with me for a bit.
Why did you call us all the way out here?
Naoi - kun, I want you to try to recover Otonashi - kun's lost memories.
Who do you think you are
Naoi - kun's hypnotism is the real deal.
He can make you regain your memories.
I would love to give that a try.
Do not just go ahead and decide that!
Do not tell me you do not want them back?
Of course I want to remember.
But why do I feel so insecure?
Is it because I might not be able to live like this if I regain my memories?
Do I enjoy living with everyone like this?
If I get my memories back, will I still be able to go on like this?
No matter what kind of past you had, do not lose sight of yourself.
No matter what happens, I will be here by your side.
I will be here too, so do not worry.
It might be fun if you go.
There is no place for kids with bad grades.
There is no way it could be fun.
Is playing with your friends fun?
It is more fun watching TV or playing games by myself.
It is a pain getting dragged around for other people's hobbies and laughing at jokes that are not even funny.
I would love to make friends too.
I do not know what I am living for.
I do not know my purpose.
I do not care about anyone else,
because it is easier to live without caring about anyone else.
Just working enough to eat and get into a daily routine...
Even so, I kept going to see my sister.
I would buy her comics with what little money I had.
I always got her whatever I picked up first at the bookstore, so I did not even know if I gave her the same one.
For all I knew, it might have been a different one, and the next part of the story was not in it.
My sister would always say that.
She would be happy with whatever I got her.
She could find her purpose in life.
But she had not been discharged for the last two years.
If only I could change places with her...
I, who did not have a purpose or meaning in life.
That compassion was what kept me visiting her.
Working during the summer is hard, but working in the winter is worse.
Your fingers go numb, like they are going to fall off.
I kept going so I could live.
If I think about it, I might stop working.
And to buy presents for my sister.
I will ask the doctor if I can take her outside on Christmas.
But she cannot use a wheelchair if there is snow on the ground...
If it is just her, I can carry her anywhere.
Then I will buy whatever she wants from any store she likes.
I want to give her a cake from a good store too.
In that case I will have to save more money.
If you could go outside on Christmas, where would you like to go?
You would be fine with just that?
But they put lights on all the trees you know!
No, I do not go there on Christmas anyway.
They say it is really pretty.
They started doing it last year.
The doctor was talking about it.
Then how about we go there?
I will ask if you can go.
Even if they say no, I will sneak you out and take you there.
That was the biggest thank you she gave me.
I would come home only to sleep.
I was working so hard because I had a goal.
My only concern was that her condition was getting worse.
They did not give her permission to leave.
So I snuck in after visiting hours ended and took her into town at night.
I am glad I came to see this too.
We will have even more fun from now on!
First I will get you a present.
I will buy anything you want.
I have saved up lots of spending money just for this day,
so I will get you anything, no matter how expensive.
How about we start by going to the store?
We could even go to a jewelers!
Or maybe you would prefer a normal department store?
And there is even more after we go shopping!
We will do dinner for now!
I do not know much about this stuff, but I got a reservation for a great restaurant I saw in a magazine.
They make a set meal for you.
After that, I continued to walk and talk by myself.
Are you sure you will be okay staying by yourself there?
If you run into any problems, tell me anytime.
You can eat here anytime you like.
Thank you for taking care of me all this time.
There was a purpose I would been living for.
I had a reason for living close by to me.
All I wanted to hear was thank you.
That was all it took for me to continue living.
I felt alive when she expressed her gratitude.
I would never noticed until now.
She was such a special person to me, and I did nothing for her.
She spent all her time in that hospital, with nothing but the comics I brought her to read.
And now that I have lost her, is my life over?
Days full of happiness that I never noticed.
and now there is nothing left for me.
Thank you for taking care of her.
I might be able to find another purpose in life.
I might discover a new meaning in living.
Devoting this life to help someone else...
Card: University Enrollment Selection Form Otonashi Yuzuru
It does not seem like it was exactly a wonderful life.
Can you leave me alone for a while?
You taught me the meaning to the pointless, worthless life I was living...
And after I found it, I died trying to reach my dream...
How could I die like that...
Have you calmed down a bit?
It is normal to become unsteady after recovering your memories.
I have realized again how strong you are.
Do you think you can carry on fighting with the Battlefront?
So you have found a purpose?
Once again, I will be in your care.
We are short on meal tickets today.
No, today's operation will be Monster Stream.
We are actually going to do it?!
There are monsters here in this world?!
Yes, the master of the river.
There is a river a short walk from here, right?
We are going to pick up food from there.
D - Do not tell me you just mean river fishing?
I got tricked into imagining something stupid again...
I wonder who will win this time?
I am looking forward to it!
Why do not you come too?
Right now we are all going river fishing.
It is against regulations to go down there.
You are not the student council president anymore so break a rule for once!
But I am still a student...
What do you think you are doing, bringing her along...
But she was still originally the student council president!
Incidentally, the current acting president is also here with us...
However, my position as God comes first.
I told you, you are not God!
She is not the student council president anymore so it is fine.
We are taking on some crazy members...
I just noticed, did no one bring any equipment?
We already contacted Guild, so it is fine.
There is someone crazy about this stuff in Guild.
He also knows about guns, but he is crazy about fishing so we call him Fish Saitou at Guild.
For this operation, he brings loads of fishing gear up with him on that cart.
He brings them all the way here?
Just how much does he like fishing...
So basically he is an idiot.
Maybe I would be your friend in this world.
There is no one like that.
It is fine if there are, right?
Even if there were, they would all disappear.
so it is okay to be friends with us.
Here, join in fishing with everyone.
That is now how you do it...
First you put a lure or bait on the hook.
You are not bothered by insects, are you...
Face the river and swing the rod with all your might!
It is because Overdrive works passively.
You might just be able to pull it off.
Reel in the master of the river!
It is a monster, like the operation name suggests.
Normally we take Monster Stream as proof of the master's anger.
When this happens we all evacuate.
We are seriously going to do this?
It is made to withstand even the master of the river!
Even so, it will be impossible like this!
What, you are going to fight with the master?
I will give you a bowl of meat udon, so help us out!
Oh my, Hinata - senpai, you are an open target!
Alright, how about I kick you with all my might?
Stop thinking up stupid things and help out!
We need more of you in the battle!
Come on you runts, cannot you pull any harder?!
If we fall like this, we will be eaten!
We are going to get swallowed!
Hey, with all this, we will not have to use Tornado for a while, right?
We are going to eat this every day?
More importantly, how are we going to preserve it?
It would not be good to waste it either...
How about we prepare it all at once and serve it to the ordinary students too?
This is almost like we are doing charity work.
We have gone from being a battlefront to some kind of volunteer group.
But we do not have an opponent to fight against anymore, so will not we stop being a battlefront?
The Slack so we do not vanish team?
I never thought we would end up doing this.
Hey Tachibana, mind if I call you by your first name?
and I have always thought from the start...
You have such a pretty name.
Kanade means to play a tune right?
If you want to take it like that, go ahead.
My name's Yuzuru, written like tie a bow.
So Kanade, I want you to do something for me.
Please stay with us from now on.
Because I do not want you to fight with anyone anymore.
I want you to enjoy your time with everyone.
Because I want to be with you too.
If you say so, I will do that.
By the way, where is Yurippe?
Now that you mention it, she has not been around...
She is probably just watching over us from somewhere.
It is not like she is the type to participate in this kind of volunteer work.
Wait, Kanade's been with me the entire time!
Which means we are closed in...
I pray we can meet again.
I cannot take on something that scary!
What is the meaning of this!?
I will tell you one possibility.
I will persuade them by force.
It appears the time has come to show you!
Leave the one's we do not make it in time for!
